column1: Baby Barnaby's////My mom got the ribeye and eggs
column2: which I must say is not actually a ribeye steak... its more like a think flank steak. Good none the less
column3: but it aint no ribeye. We shared one of the blueberry pancakes
column5: it came out just right. I had the green eggs which came with that fantastic chicken apple sausage
column7: and these potato things. The eggs were delish
column8: sausage was great which is a big deal for me considering I don't really like sausage
column10: but those potato home fries/tator tots/hash brown thingies were just not that great to me.
